name: (3S)-3-Acetyl-3-benzyl-5-hydroxy-6,7-dimethoxy-4-methyl-1-benzofuran-2(3H)-one

The methoxy groups increase the melting point due to the increased molecular weight and van der Waals forces, estimated at around +10°C each.
